      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains in great shape with no major stains or tears. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a solid service history, though it may soon require standard preventative maintenance like new brake pads. You can expect a comfortable, reliable ride that looks sharp on the road without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
