      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint shows some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, but the body remains straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean with some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, though it will eventually need standard wear-and-tear items like brake pads replaced in the next few thousand miles. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car ready for its next owner.",
